{"id": 608, "genre": 1001, "title": "你买bra遇到的最大问题是什么？", "description": "店里买太贵，代购码不准。", "record_count": 6919, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130124N4zEiS5skfXmcuRO.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-02T12:23:11Z", "options": [{"id": 21760, "content": "大码胸衣太成熟，配套内裤太性感，试衣房间太低端。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 59992}, {"id": 21765, "content": "要么长胖，要么变瘦，bra是要换一打的节奏么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281379}, {"id": 24069, "content": "不要尴尬到被人摸胸后，凹下去，再也没有凸起来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 295375}, {"id": 22792, "content": "总有热心的店员过来把胸捏来捏去= =", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 288568}, {"id": 22794, "content": "店员热心帮忙试穿 然后眼睁睁看着rt从半杯边露出来… ", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 288568}, {"id": 44555, "content": "因为胸不够大被店员推荐超厚款", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290302}, {"id": 21772, "content": "陪女朋友逛内衣店总是进退两难", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163257}, {"id": 21774, "content": "从未买到正真合适的内衣，属于底盘较大胸型，挤沟会压胸，有的钢圈又会卡胸，肩带会一直掉。实体店价格太高，和导购会帮你弄胸实在也是受不了，网购尺码舒适也是大问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281554}, {"id": 21775, "content": "成套内衣是不是得配三条内裤才合理？不是说内衣不能常洗么？但内裤得天天换啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281554}, {"id": 21778, "content": "说自己贴合的不贴合 说自己聚拢的不聚拢 老是前胸线空出一道痕 怪我咯", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248869}, {"id": 21779, "content": "每次去68总有妹子带着自己的男朋友，我选的bra都被别人男朋友看到了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281584}, {"id": 21782, "content": "好不容易在实体店买了件平时穿的码，试穿的时候还算杠杠的，回家后过了一点时间去穿，发现怎么这么紧。。我这二十好几的年纪该不会。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202356}, {"id": 21783, "content": "没有女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183222}, {"id": 21784, "content": "舒服的小bra永远贵得难以置信", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281664}, {"id": 21786, "content": "我就推荐奇丽尔，平价好穿 。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168954}, {"id": 23074, "content": "胸太小都不好意进内衣店 所以从来不尴尬◉‿◉", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289992}, {"id": 23842, "content": "总是不敢买，怕销售说我变态，我男的", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294023}, {"id": 24101, "content": "胸小想买无钢圈 但贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296613}, {"id": 23851, "content": "永远买不到真正合适且舒适的bra", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294083}, {"id": 25131, "content": "一大一小怎么破。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305964}, {"id": 45612, "content": "没胸，不穿吧不好，穿吧又太多余", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450692}, {"id": 22829, "content": "搁不下～", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281491}, {"id": 23088, "content": "不好意思我们这款只做到C", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290446}, {"id": 21821, "content": "从来没有百分百满意-_-#", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278522}, {"id": 24129, "content": "你好你", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 297233}, {"id": 24899, "content": "小到没码", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304677}, {"id": 21830, "content": "因为胸大永远是大妈款…(︶^︶)", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281346}, {"id": 23623, "content": "太小买不到合适的", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274922}, {"id": 25934, "content": "胸小", "image": null, "prai